I have to be all social and stuff for the next few days, so the process of making myself a ghetto nuclear physicist will have to take a brief hiatus.  Never fear, I will figure out some answers for folks about neutron moderation and other issues soon enough.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
