Very little.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Actually, it may not even BE oxygen.  I was just suggesting the possible presence of an opacity agent.  Tungsten has been suggested, but oxygen is nicely benign, so I would like for it to be that.<br>
