pace.showUserPublicProfile?gid=whitestar60>whitestar60</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>NEP Freighter Crewman</span><br>  Posts: 58<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/3/02 8:43:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=133.topic&index=93>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.b5tech.net/art/b5/vorlonangry.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: no moderator?</span><hr size=1> *starts saving for a seat on the first liberty launch<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/bnuclearspace.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mauk2>Mauk2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>NERVA Spaceplane Pilot</span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/5/02 1:13:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=133.topic&index=94>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: no moderator?</span><hr size=1> Okay, I have been a busy boy, so hang onto yer kidneys.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
